      *                      * Stampa                                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      18                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      057                  to   p-pos                  .
